==========================================
IF RAW SOURCE:

autoreconf --install
./configure
make

===========================================
IF PACKAGE:

To build and install:

./configure
make
make install

To find out more on how to use the SPHERLS packages see user manuals in ./docs/manuals

============================================
COMMON OPTIONS

for debugging configurations do 

  ./configure CXXFLAGS="-g -O0"

instead of the regular ./configure